                <h4 class= "services-title group">Lean Six Sigma Executive Investment Questionnaire</h4>
                <p class= "">This ISCEA backed study is focused upon the concept that Lean Six Sigma should have a more critical eye from investors and key company executives.
This study focuses on metrics that support the concept that executives should know when to start, stop or re-invest into a company-wide Lean Six Sigma initiative.
The results of the study will be presented in an annual study and report for those executives involved.</p>
<a href="mailto:uta.raidlabs@gmail.com?subject=Lean Six Sigma Executive Investment Questionnaire">More info</a>
